                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1 features-text">
                    <small>INSPINIA</small>
                    <h2>Perfectly designed </h2>
                    <i class="fa fa-clock-o big-icon pull-right"></i>
